            Description = "Example Deployment Strategy",

            GrowthFactor = 10,
            GrowthType = "LINEAR",
            ReplicateTo = "NONE",
            Tags =

                { "Type", "AppConfig Deployment Strategy" },
            },
        });
    }

}

        <span class="property-indicator"></span>

    <dd><p>A description of the deployment strategy. Can be at most 1024 characters.</p>

            title="Optional">

</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">Integer</span>
    </dt>
    <dd><p>The amount of time AWS AppConfig monitors for alarms before considering the deployment to be complete and no longer eligible for automatic roll back. Minimum value of 0, maximum value of 1440.</p>
</dd><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span id="state_growthfactor_java">

        <span class="property-type">Double</span>
    </dt>
    <dd><p>The percentage of targets to receive a deployed configuration during each interval. Minimum value of 1.0, maximum value of 100.0.</p>

## Import



AppConfig Deployment Strategies can be imported by using their deployment strategy ID, e.g.,

```sh
 $ pulumi import aws:appconfig/deploymentStrategy:DeploymentStrategy example 11xxxxx
```
